staff.<\/h2><p class=\"lg9-copy\">Service alerts route to the staff touchscreen monitor while QR orders print to a dedicated PoolSafe printer. Those are separate paths, which keeps the operational workflow clear.<\/p><\/div><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Designed for operators<\/h3><ul style=\"margin:16px 0 0;padding-left:20px;color:#466170;line-height:1.75;\"><li>Guest requests stay visible to staff without guesswork<\/li><li>Ordering stays close to the seat in 2.0<\/li><li>Each tier adds capability without replacing the previous one<\/li><\/ul><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-rowlayout kb-row-layout-wrap kb-row-layout-id-lg-feat-fitbyproperty lg9-section lg9-soft\"><div class=\"kt-row-column-wrap kt-has-1-columns kt-gutter-default kt-v-gutter-default kt-row-valign-top kt-row-layout-equal kt-tab-layout-row kt-m-colapse-left-to-right kt-mobile-layout-row kt-inner-column-height-default\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-kadence-column inner-column-1\"><div class=\"kt-inside-inner-col\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-shell has-global-padding is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained\"><p class=\"lg9-kicker\">Where Each Tier Fits<\/p><h2 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-md\">Match the rollout to the seating zone, service model, and guest expectation.<\/h2><div class=\"wp-block-columns lg9-grid-3 is-layout-flex wp-container-core-columns-is-layout-28f84493 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\"><div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\"><div class=\"wp-block-group lg9-card lg9-card-soft is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow\"><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading lg9-title-sm\">Classic<\/h3><p class=\"lg9-copy\">A fit for premium seating areas that need a stronger guest experience first, before ad